<h4 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center">Summary</h4>



<ul>
<li>Astronaught is a Exploration Tower Defense game where you gather resources and explore with your spaceship during the day and gather resources to upgrade your ship. At night, fight enemies with your upgraded ship and gather BioFuel from dead enemies. The objective of the game is to reach the BioFuel goal and escape the planet. </li>



<li>Developed for Epic MegaJam 2023. Made in Unreal Engine 5.</li>



<li>Part of a team of 5 as one of the programmers</li>



<li>In charge of resource and building spawning system and resource gathering system</li>
</ul>
