<div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow" style="flex-basis:60%">
<p class="has-text-align-left">I developed the resource and building spawning system for the game. We wanted resource areas and buildings to spawn around the player. So, I made a system where in the beginning of the game, resource areas and buildings will spawn around the player in a circle around the spaceship. On a new day, old resource areas will despawn and respawn around the spaceship. Resource Areas will not spawn close around the spacesghip but will spawn outside of a certain radius that can be modified. On the gif that shows the early stages of resource spawning, the red debug sphere shows the area where the resource area won&#8217;t spawn and the green debug sphere is the extents of the spawn area.</p>
