<div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow" style="flex-basis:60%">
<p>The player resource gathering system was also made by me. It was simple as we were using the Gameplay Ability System (GAS) as all I had to do was make an ability that activates by pressing right click. The ability does a sphere trace around the player and collects resources as long as the player is holding the button. The collection stops when the player lets go of the button or the player goes out of range.</p>
